        "title": "The Exchange",
        "description": "When you save the one who matters to you by condemning others to the fate you pulled them from — leave the rest of the prisoners behind, hand over civilians to secure your crew's release, sacrifice a community's future to rescue a single life."
      },
      "advanceTrigger": "When someone whose fate was sealed is free because of your actions — not a close call in combat, but a rescue from a situation with no way out.",
